      "data": {
        "text": "- users can set their preference (age, gender, etc)\n- users can view a \"stack\" of potential matches\n    - match preferences\n    - close to current location\n- user can swipe left (no) / right (yes)\n- 2 users swipe right, match -> notification\n\noos\n- creating a full profile\n \n\nConstraint\n- Avoid showing repeat profiles\n\n\nScale\n- 10M DAU\n\n\nNon-functional Requirements\n- Consistency for swipes\n- Low latency stack loading (<300ms)\n- Scale to handle the high write throughput of 10M * 100 swipes a day.\n\n\n\nCore Entities\n\n- Profile\n- Swipe\n- Match",
